eam\n!width=65%|Qualifying method\n!width=15%|App {{small|(Last)}}\n|-\n|{{flagicon|QAT}}\n|[[2019\u201320 Qatar Stars League]] champions\n|\n|-\n|{{flagicon|QAT}}\n|[[2020 Emir of Qatar Cup]] winners\n|\n|-\n|{{flagicon|QAT}}\n|[[2019\u201320 Qatar Stars League]] runners-up\n|\n|-\n|{{flagicon|KSA}}\n|[[2019\u201320 Saudi Professional League]] champions\n|\n|-\n|{{flagicon|KSA}}\n|[[2019\u201320 King Cup]] winners\n|\n|-\n|{{flagicon|KSA}}\n|[[2019\u201320 Saudi Professional League]] runners-up\n|\n|-\n|{{flagicon|IRN}}\n|[[2019\u201320 Persian Gulf Pro League]] champions\n|\n|-\n|{{flagicon|IRN}}\n|[[2019\u201320 Hazfi Cup]] winners\n|\n|-\n|{{flagicon|UAE}}\n|[[2019\u201320 UAE Pro League]] champions\n|\n|-\n|{{flagicon|UAE}}\n|[[2019\u201320 UAE President's Cup]] winners\n|\n|-\n|{{flagicon|IRQ}}\n|[[2019\u201320 Iraqi Premier League]] champions\n|\n|-\n|{{flagicon|UZB}}\n|[[2020 Uzbekistan Super League]] champions\n|\n|-\n|{{flagicon|JOR}}\n|[[2020 Jordanian Pro League]] champions\n|\n|-\n|{{flagicon|IND}} [[FC Goa]]\n|[[2019\u201320 Indian Super League season#Regular season|2019\u201320 Indian Super League regular season]] winners\n|1st\n|-\n|{{flagicon|TJK}}\n|[[2020 Tajikistan Higher League]] champions\n|\n|-\n|{{flagicon|TKM}}\n|[[2020 \u00ddokary Liga]] champions\n|\n|}\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"table-layout:fixed;width:100%;\"\n|+[[#Qualifying play-offs|Qualifying play-off]] participants\n|-\n!width=20%|Team\n!width=65%|Qualifying method\n!width=15%|App {{small|(Last)}}\n|-\n|{{flagicon|QAT}}\n|[[2019\u201320 Qatar Stars League]] 3rd place\n|\n|-\n|{{flagicon|KSA}}\n|[[2019\u201320 Saudi Professional League]] 3rd place\n|\n|-\n|{{flagicon|IRN}}\n|[[2019\u201320 Persian Gulf Pro League]] runners-up\n|\n|-\n|{{flagicon|IRN}}\n|[[2019\u201320 Persian Gulf Pro League]] 3rd place\n|\n|-\n|{{flagicon|UAE}}\n|[[2019\u201320 UAE Pro League]] runners-up\n|\n|-\n|{{flagicon|UAE}}\n|[[2019\u201320 UAE Pro League]] 3rd place\n|\n|-\n|{{flagicon|IRQ}}\n|[[2019\u